    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/01/HA/HA054.ogg"
    hachiman "You're quite open-minded, huh..."
    hachiman "(But then, you'd need to have someone to confess to first.)"
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/01/YI/YI065.ogg"
    yui "No, I mean... I'm not sure if I'm really decisive enough when it comes down to it, so I was wondering if you could give me that push. Tahaha...!"
    stop music fadeout 1.0
    jump E3_YUI_06

