    hachiman "H-Happy Birthday."
    show yui school mid_center vhappy at left with dissolve
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/06/YI/YI011.ogg"
    yui "Before, we didn't manage to celebrate it properly. So I wanted to do it again, so I talked with Hikki about it."
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/06/HA/HA006.ogg"
    hachiman "Yeah, that's right."
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/06/YK/YK006.ogg"
    yukino "Hikigaya-kun... Yuigahama-san... What should I say...?"
    show yukino school mid_left vhappy at right with dissolve
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/06/YK/YK007.ogg"
    yukino "Having someone celebrate it for me like this... It's the first time for me. So... Really... Thank you."
    show yui school mid_right blush at left with dissolve:
