    show yukino school near_center vhappy with dissolve
    voice "audio/voice/E3/YUI/07/YK/YK007.ogg"
    yukino "Yeah, I'm okay, really. So you don't have to be so bothered about it, in fact, isn't it better for Hayama-kun if you didn't mind it so much?"
